Question: Dongguan Zhongjin Electronics Technology Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Dongguan Zhongjin Electronics Technology Co., Ltd

Power Supply Products

- Offers a wide range of power supply products such as 5W, 6W, 9W, 12W, 15W, 18W, 25W, 36W, 42W, 48W, 65W, and 100W
- Products achieved international certifications of UL, ETL, GS, CE, PSE, SAA, RCM, KC, IRAM, BS, CB, FCC, EMC
- Complies with RoHS, Reach, and PAHS standards to ensure product safety and environmental friendliness.
